does it dump the flo and underlay flo data files as well?

It’s modern. Most of the files in here are formatted differently than the older cache (414 <) and since it works for 414 - current Runescape I can’t make a reliable hash dictionary and expect it to rename the files correctly. But yes it dumps EVERYTHING. I mean that too lol. The 508 cache has over 300k files in it.

If you are interested in how the newer files are formatted, I have a couple threads lying around that I can find. One being how the musics are formatted…
